# Design Decisions for Lab 5

## Approach
- Used provided CSS variables for color consistency and easy theming.
- Started with basic structure and gradually added transitions, shadows, and hover states.
- Ensured all components are responsive and mobile-friendly using media queries.
- Used semantic HTML for accessibility.

## Challenges
- Making cards look modern without using frameworks.
- Getting the navigation bar to look good and be flexible on mobile.
- Ensuring button variants are visually distinct but consistent.

## Resources
- MDN CSS Reference
- CSS Tricks
